  </ul>

  <h2>Skills</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Python, Java, HTML/CSS</li>
    <li>Git, Docker</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Projects</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Resume Builder — simple web app that generates PDF resumes</li>
    <li>Todo App — CRUD app with local storage</li>
  </ul>

</body>
</html>




#commands
docker build -t resume-app .
docker run -p 8080:80 resume-app
http://localhost:8080


